Simplify the cleanup logic a bit.

Signed-off-by: Thomas Wei√üschuh <linux@weissschuh.net>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20240904-acpi-battery-cleanups-v1-3-a3bf74f22d40@weissschuh.net
